oglobin-inducing agents.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/63189/', '', 'Artesunate, Mefloquine, Lumefantrine, Artemether, Pyrimethamine, Atovaquone, Hydroxychloroquine, Halofantrine, Proguanil', '', 1767369485);
